       01 G2.
         02 X           PIC XX.
         02 Y           REDEFINES X.
           03 A         PIC X OCCURS 1 TO 2 DEPENDING ON I.
       01 G3.
         02 X.
           03 A         PIC X OCCURS 1 TO 2 DEPENDING ON I.
